        {
            "title": "黃金價格企穩,因伊朗戰爭削弱降息預期而面臨單週深度虧損",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.8U7o2y_GbdgFiUKgSfZAg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEB0P0G3_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 黃金價格週五在亞洲交易時段企穩,但正承受六年來最嚴重的單週跌幅,原因是美國與以色列對伊朗的戰爭提高了通脹預期,並削弱了市場對降息的押注。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在多家主要央行對伊朗戰爭的通脹影響發出警告後,黃金週四暴跌。這反過來加劇了市場對近期不會降息的預期——這種情況對貴金屬來說是個壞消息。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至美國東部時間20:45(北京時間00:45),現貨黃金上漲0.1%至4,655.74美元/盎司,而黃金期貨上漲1.2%至4,659.46美元/盎司。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-6a2a1bb2-e3b6-373d-90a8-c6aab1cc728c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">現貨黃金本週交易下跌近8%——這是自2020年初以來最嚴重的單週跌幅。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">黃金被廣泛視為避險資產,但自2月下旬伊朗戰爭爆發以來,其表現一直大幅落後。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本週的跌勢使黃金跌破了自戰爭開始以來一直維持的5,000美元至5,200美元/盎司的交易區間。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由於市場擔憂衝突的通脹影響,美元和美國國債收益率飆升,大大蓋過了流入黃金的避險資金。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本週油價飆升至近四年高位,尤其是在中東能源基礎設施遭到襲擊後,顯示供應將進一步中斷。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">油價飆升促使一系列全球主要央行對能源驅動的通脹發出警告。澳洲儲備銀行加息,而聯準會、歐洲央行、瑞士國家銀行和日本央行均維持利率不變,並警告未來幾個月不會有太多變化。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">其他貴金屬週五回落,本週也面臨下跌。現貨白銀下跌0.2%至72.683美元/盎司,而現貨鉑金下跌0.4%至1,967.63美元/盎司。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">白銀和鉑金本週分別下跌9.8%和2.9%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E4%BC%81%E7%A9%A9-%E5%9B%A0%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E6%88%B0%E7%88%AD%E5%89%8A%E5%BC%B1%E9%99%8D%E6%81%AF%E9%A0%90%E6%9C%9F%E8%80%8C%E9%9D%A2%E8%87%A8%E5%96%AE%E9%80%B1%E6%B7%B1%E5%BA%A6%E8%99%A7%E6%90%8D-015800651.html",
